flowRoot.flowPara: EARTH STRIKE
Educating and Engaging
citizens by reaching out to local communities, distributing educational materials, and helping others get involved through direct action.
OUR PLAN
Our protests and rallies, scheduled throughout 2019, are raising awareness for a GLOBAL GENERAL STRIKE beginning September 27.
The companies and politicians
are destroying our planet.
But they are few in number,
and it is our compliance in the system
that keeps them afloat.
To prepare for our strike, we will educate, engage,
and assist our local communities through:
Demonstrating
at public events worldwide, to spread our message and train our communities in boots-on-the-ground activism.
Providing a Platform
for leading environmental activists to share their visions for the future of climate activism.
Connecting
with other environmental activist groups to form a worldwide network and unify the global environmental cause.
Providing Mutual Aid
for those who are already victims of climate change, and will continue to be victimized in the future by its wide-ranging effects.
Naming and Shaming
corporate executives who contribute to environmental destruction, and politicians who fail to regulate them effectively.
